'''主權投票系統公司'''是一家總部分別設在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]]和[[美國|美國]][[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]]<ref name=":6">{{Cite news|last1=Zuidijk|first1=Daniel|last2=Mehrotra|first2=Kartikay|date=2020-11-17|title=Trump Lashes Voting Tech Firm With Barrage of Debunked Claims|language=en|work=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-17/trump-s-election-attacks-put-voting-tech-firm-in-the-crosshairs|access-date=2020-11-22|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120113520/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-17/trump-s-election-attacks-put-voting-tech-firm-in-the-crosshairs}}</ref>專門生產[[電子投票|電子投票]]硬件和軟件的私人企業<ref name=dvs>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapid=46054856|title=Company Overview of Dominion Voting Systems Corporation|date=2017-06-21|website=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|access-date=2017-06-21|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115030151/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=e8c7c410-26ee-11eb-a4ff-a139431008a9&url=L3Jlc2VhcmNoL3N0b2Nrcy9wcml2YXRlL3NuYXBzaG90LmFzcD9wcml2Y2FwaWQ9NDYwNTQ4NTY=}}</ref>，它也為加拿大、美國和[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]等國家的企業製作公司內部用軟件<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|last=Thibodeau|first=Patrick|date=2016-11-05|title=One election-system vendor uses developers in Serbia|url=https://www.computerworld.com/article/3126791/one-election-system-vendor-uses-developers-in-serbia.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115030004/https://www.computerworld.com/article/3126791/one-election-system-vendor-uses-developers-in-serbia.html|archive-date=2020-11-15|access-date=2019-06-27|website={{link-en|電腦世界|Computerworld}}|language=en}}</ref>。

主權投票系統的投票機讓選民可以進行電子投票，其{{le|光學素描投票系統|Optical scan voting system|光學素描投票機}}對選票進行自動計票<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://verifiedvoting.org/election-system/dominion-imagecast-evolution/ |title=ImageCast Evolution |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201063248/https://verifiedvoting.org/election-system/dominion-imagecast-evolution/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://verifiedvoting.org/election-system/dominion-imagecast-x/ |title=ImageCast X |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201063142/https://verifiedvoting.org/election-system/dominion-imagecast-x/}}</ref>。美國和加拿大都有應用主權投票機進行不同規模的投票活動，例如加拿大的第一大黨黨魁選舉和[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]中其中28州的選民投票<ref name=".newsweek_1547405">{{Cite news|last=Roos|first=Meghan|date=2020-11-13|url=https://www.newsweek.com/dominion-voting-systems-categorically-denies-election-tech-glitches-following-trump-accusations-1547405|title=Dominion Voting Systems "categorically denies" election tech glitches following Trump accusations|work=[[新聞周刊|新聞周刊]]|access-date=2020-11-25|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201063142/https://www.newsweek.com/dominion-voting-systems-categorically-denies-election-tech-glitches-following-trump-accusations-1547405}}</ref>。

其中於2020年美國總統大選中，當[[喬·拜登|喬·拜登]]在11月的選民投票中贏得足夠的州分後，尋求連任的對手[[唐納德·特朗普|唐納德·特朗普]]和他的支持者開始對主權投票系統進行一連串舞弊指控，例如主權投票系統公司有份直接參與選舉舞弊、或其軟件有安全漏洞能讓第三者篡改上百萬張選票，這些指控都被不同選舉技術專家、政府官員、選舉業員工和{{le|網絡安全和基礎設施安全局|Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency|網絡安全和基礎設施安全局（CISA）}}指為缺乏實質證據支持的[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|last=Collins|first=Ben|date=2020-11-13|title=QAnon's Dominion voter fraud conspiracy theory reaches the president|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/q-fades-qanon-s-dominion-voter-fraud-conspiracy-theory-reaches-n1247780|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115030155/https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/q-fades-qanon-s-dominion-voter-fraud-conspiracy-theory-reaches-n1247780|archive-date=2020-11-15|access-date=2020-11-14|website=[[NBC新聞|NBC新聞]]}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|last=Nicas|first=Jack|date=2020-11-11|title=No, Dominion voting machines did not delete Trump votes|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/11/technology/no-dominion-voting-machines-did-not-cause-widespread-voting-problems.html|access-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115030030/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/11/technology/no-dominion-voting-machines-did-not-delete-trump-votes.html|archive-date=2020-11-15}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|last1=Tucker|first1=Eric|last2=Bajak|first2=Frank|date=2020-11-13|title=Repudiating Trump, officials say election 'most secure'|url=https://apnews.com/article/top-officials-elections-most-secure-66f9361084ccbc461e3bbf42861057a5|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115030026/https://apnews.com/article/top-officials-elections-most-secure-66f9361084ccbc461e3bbf42861057a5|archive-date=2020-11-15|access-date=2020-11-14|website=[[美聯社|美聯社]]}}</ref>。由於[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]和[[威斯康星州|威斯康星州]]的兩位候選人的得票差在允許要求重新點票的範圍內，因此特朗普要求這兩個州以人手進行點票，最後人手點票與最初利用了主權投票系統進行的電子點票的結果只有非常細微而不影響選舉結果的誤差，拜登依然獲確認贏得這兩個關鍵州<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/17/georgia-says-voting-machine-audit-found-no-evidence-of-fraud-tampering.html|title=Georgia says voting machine audit found no evidence of fraud or tampering|first=Thomas|last=Franck|date=2020-11-17|work=[[全國廣播公司商業頻道|全國廣播公司商業頻道]]|access-date=2020-11-25|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201063200/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/17/georgia-says-voting-machine-audit-found-no-evidence-of-fraud-tampering.html}}</ref>。

主權投票系統公司在2020年12月至2021年1月間對[[福斯新聞|福斯新聞]]、[[福斯財經網|福斯財經網]]、[[大全新聞|大全新聞]]和{{le|美國思想家|American Thinker}}等保守派媒體發出律師信，要求停止對其公司進行不實的選舉舞弊指控，否則就會控告這些媒體[[誹謗|誹謗]]<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|last=Feldman|first=Josh|date=2020-12-18|title=Lou Dobbs Airs Stunning Fact-Check of His Own Election Claims|url=https://www.mediaite.com/tv/lou-dobbs-airs-stunning-fact-check-of-his-own-election-conspiracies-after-company-threatens-legal-action/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107042912/https://www.mediaite.com/tv/lou-dobbs-airs-stunning-fact-check-of-his-own-election-conspiracies-after-company-threatens-legal-action/|archive-date=2021-01-07|access-date=2021-02-01|website=[[Mediaite|Mediaite]]}}</ref><ref name=":9">{{Cite web|last=Feldman|first=Josh|date=2020-12-20|title=Maria Bartiromo Airs Fact-Check, Adds 'We Will Keep Investigating'|url=https://www.mediaite.com/tv/maria-bartiromo-airs-same-fact-check-of-election-conspiracies-as-fox-colleagues-adds-we-will-keep-investigating/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111033201/https://www.mediaite.com/tv/maria-bartiromo-airs-same-fact-check-of-election-conspiracies-as-fox-colleagues-adds-we-will-keep-investigating/|archive-date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-02-01|website=[[Mediaite|Mediaite]]}}</ref><ref name=":10">{{Cite web|last=Barr|first=Jeremy|date=2021-01-21|title=Newsmax issues sweeping 'clarification' debunking its own coverage of election misinformation|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/media/2020/12/21/newsmax-clarification-smartmatic/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221235729/https://www.washingtonpost.com/media/2020/12/21/newsmax-clarification-smartmatic/|archive-date=2020-12-21|access-date=2020-12-22|website=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]}}</ref><ref name=":12">{{Cite news|last=Corasaniti|first=Nick|date=2021-01-25|title=Rudy Giuliani Sued by Dominion Voting Systems Over False Election Claims|language=en-US|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/25/us/politics/rudy-giuliani-dominion-trump.html|access-date=2021-01-25|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125122130/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/25/us/politics/rudy-giuliani-dominion-trump.html}}</ref>。主權投票系統公司又於1月對支持特朗普的律師[[西德尼·鮑威爾|西德尼·鮑威爾]]和[[魯迪·朱利安尼|魯迪·朱利安尼]]控告誹謗，並對兩人各索償13億美元以彌補聲譽損害<ref name=":11">{{Cite news|last=Brown|first=Emma|date=2021-01-08|title=Dominion sues pro-Trump lawyer Sidney Powell, seeking more than $1.3 billion|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/dominion-sues-pro-trump-lawyer-sidney-powell-seeking-more-than-13-billion/2021/01/08/ebe5dbe0-5106-11eb-b96e-0e54447b23a1_story.html|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109052840/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/dominion-sues-pro-trump-lawyer-sidney-powell-seeking-more-than-13-billion/2021/01/08/ebe5dbe0-5106-11eb-b96e-0e54447b23a1_story.html}}</ref><ref name=":13">{{cite news|last=Polantz|first=Katelyn|date=2021-01-25|title=Dominion sues Giuliani for $1.3 billion over 'Big Lie'|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/25/politics/dominion-lawsuit-giuliani/index.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220522062242/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/25/politics/dominion-lawsuit-giuliani/index.html|archive-date=2022-05-22|access-date=2021-01-25|website=[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]]}}</ref>，及後[[同一個美國新聞網|同一個美國新聞網]]將所有指控主權投票系統和{{le|Smartmatic}}的選舉舞弊資訊從網站上撤下，同一個美國新聞網並沒有發表任何關於移除資訊的啟事<ref>{{Cite web|last=Shamsian|first=Jacob|date=2021-01-21|title=Trump-ally media outlet OAN quietly deleted articles about Dominion despite publicly doubling down on election conspiracy theories|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/oan-deletes-articles-about-dominion-voting-election-conspiracy-2021-1|access-date=2021-01-29|website=[[商業內幕|商業內幕]]|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120212821/https://www.businessinsider.com/oan-deletes-articles-about-dominion-voting-election-conspiracy-2021-1}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Thalen|first=Mikael|date=2021-01-21|title=Pro-Trump outlet OAN is deleting all its articles about Dominion|url=https://www.dailydot.com/debug/pro-trump-outlet-oan-is-deleting-all-its-articles-about-dominion/|access-date=2021-01-29|website=[[The_Daily_Dot|The Daily Dot]]|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121194901/https://www.dailydot.com/debug/pro-trump-outlet-oan-is-deleting-all-its-articles-about-dominion/}}</ref>。2021年3月，主權投票系統公司對福斯新聞提出16億美元誹謗索償<ref name=":14">{{Cite news|last=Izadi|first=Elahe|date=2021-03-26|title=Fox News sued by Dominion Voting for $1.6 billion over election fraud claims|language=en-US|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/media/2021/03/26/fox-dominion-lawsuit-defamation/|access-date=2021-03-26|issn=0190-8286|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326155159/https://www.washingtonpost.com/media/2021/03/26/fox-dominion-lawsuit-defamation/}}</ref>。

